MS NID 16/17

Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Sans Hebrew SemiCondensed ExtraLight' ≠ 'Noto Sans Hebrew SemCond ExtLt' (NID 1).

Noto Sans Hebrew SemCond Light Regular (NotoSansHebrew-SemiCondensedLight.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Sans Hebrew SemiCondensed Light' ≠ 'Noto Sans Hebrew SemCond Light' (NID 1).
